    Reposting: Survey on Experiences during Online and Remote Learning

    by Mary Joy Villamora - Thursday, 15 September 2022, 8:09 AM

    Dear G8 - G12 scholars,

    Warm greetings!

    Mr. Rex S. Forteza, a graduate student of Korea National University of Education (KNUE) and a faculty member of the Philippine Science High School - Central Luzon Campus, is currently gathering data about the online and remote experiences in PSHS campuses. This would require a survey from G8-G12 student participants.

    Interested scholars are asked to fill out this week an online survey questionnaire (accessible through https://tinyurl.com/pisayTD). The information you share may also help improve our school and other schools. Plus, Beats Studio Buds worth Php 9,000 will be raffled to those who will participate and complete the online survey. The winner will be drawn this November 2022. 

    Thank you very much!

    For Grade 8 to 12 scholars

    by Riza Reyna Calma - Thursday, 8 September 2022, 2:02 PM

    Magandang araw sa lahat.

    Nangangailangan ng limang mag-aaral bawat seksyon (Grade 8 - Grade 12) upang sumagot sa survey para sa research ni Mr. Rex S. Forteza, guro ng PSHS - CLC na may pamagat na Influence of Transaction Distance on Student Engagement in Remote and Online K-12 Learning Environment (kasalukuyang nag-aaral si Mr. Forteza sa Korea National University of Education ) sa ibaba makikita ang link.

    https://tinycurl.com/PisayTD

    Malaki ang maitutulong nito para makita ang ating sitwasyon sa ating remote noong nakaraan at online environment.

    Maraming salamat.
